.el .ds Aq '
.TH dkp-build 1  "build 0.1.1" 
.SH NAME
dkp\-build \- Package a pack into a versioned archive with checksums.json
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdkp build\fR [\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-out\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-human\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-audience\fR] [\fB\-\-gen\-mcp\-manifest\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIPACK\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Package a pack into a versioned archive with checksums.json
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR \fI<FMT>\fR [default: zip]
Archive format: zip | tar.gz
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: plain]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
plain: Human\-readable plain text (default)
.IP \(bu 2
table: Aligned table using comfy\-table
.IP \(bu 2
json: Pretty\-printed JSON
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-out\fR \fI<DIR>\fR
Output directory (default: build/)
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress informational output; print only results
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-human\fR
Exclude human/ assets (machine\-only distribution)
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print debug info (schema paths, provider calls, etc.)
.TP
\fB\-\-audience\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Filter content to assets tagged for a specific audience profile
.TP
\fB\-\-gen\-mcp\-manifest\fR
Regenerate machine/mcp_manifest.json before packaging
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
<\fIPACK\fR>
Path to the DKP bundle directory
.SH VERSION
v0.1.1
